headline: TD Cowen Keeps Buy Rating on Fiserv (FI) Following Forum Event
summary: Fiserv, Inc. (NYSE:FI) is one of the 12 Best Fintech Stocks to Buy According to Analysts. On October 1, TD Cowen reaffirmed its Buy rating with a $188 price target for Fiserv, Inc. (NYSE:FI). This decision follows Fiserv, Inc.’s (NYSE:FI) Forum 2025 event, which showcased the company’s innovation and unification plans. TD Cowen believes these […]
